    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i look in the mirror and i dont even recognize the person looking back. it feels like the real me, the person who actually had dreams and a life, died a long time ago. i'm just going through the motions now. like i'm a ghost or a walking corpse just inhabiting a body that shouldve been gone years ago.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
